-----------------------------------------------------------
Server
-----------------------------------------------------------
sudo apt-get install lib2cap-bin
sudo setcap cap_net_bind_service=+ep `readlink -f \`which node\``
pm2 start app.js 		- start running a server permanently


-----------------------------------------------------------
Mongo
-----------------------------------------------------------
sudo service mongod start 	- start mongo db
mongo 				- run mongo

-----------------------------------------------------------
NPM
-----------------------------------------------------------

npm init			- create package.json
npm install			- install dependencies

-----------------------------------------------------------
Git
-----------------------------------------------------------

git commit -m "My message"
git stash 			- push changes like on a stack
git stash pop			- merge changes
git clone <repo to clone>
git checkout --			- if local dir fucked up, download global from github


-----------------------------------------------------------
Others
-----------------------------------------------------------
Xampp (Mysql server)		- sudo /opt/lampp/manager-linux-x64.run 

